          .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
            %h2.text-center.l-margin-bottom
              Join our team
            %p
              Here at LearnSignal, we like proactive innovators who produce great work and play an impactful role in interesting projects. Our passion is to make education a better experience for individuals and businesses, and we are looking for individuals with the same mindset.
            %p
              We are a small team of passionate people working in a challenging environment. Everyone makes an impact. Everyone has the opportunity to showcase their talent. We like to practice what we preach. We're always learning and expanding our knowledge. If there’s something you want to learn or a course you want to take, we have you covered. We work in a beautiful office in the centre of Dublin, and we’re flexible with hours worked in the office.

            %hr/

          .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
            %p
              As a dedicated training resource we are always on the lookout for talent. If you possess the required qualifications along with extensive experience in finance, IT or business, and are passionate about teaching, we’d love to hear from you.
            %p
              LearnSignal is an evolving company and is looking to expand its services, so if you are a specialist in a certain subject or area and think you could add value to our course curriculum, we are open to proposals. In return, we’ll provide you and your course with exposure to individuals and businesses who are actively seeking professional development. It’s a win win.
            %p
              Use the contact form below and one of our team will get in touch with you to discuss further teaching opportunities with LearnSignal.

